Description: Download and aggregate data from all public hire bicycle systems
    which provide open data, currently including 'Santander' Cycles in London,
    U.K.; from the U.S.A., 'Ford GoBike' in San Francisco CA, 'citibike' in New
    York City NY, 'Divvy' in Chicago IL, 'Capital Bikeshare' in Washington DC,
    'Hubway' in Boston MA, 'Metro' in Los Angeles LA, 'Indego' in Philadelphia
    PA, and 'Nice Ride' in Minnesota; 'Bixi' from Montreal, Canada; and 'mibici'
    from Guadalajara, Mexico.
